data.description: Welcome Home to the highly desired community of Astoria! With resort-style amenities just steps away from this gorgeous newer home, the expressway being so close by, and a fully fenced yard - this location could not be more perfect! With a newer home that was the neighborhood model home, you have all newer construction and new plumbing and electrical of course! And there has also been a new 4th bedroom added last year along with all brand new appliances and a new outdoor kitchen! NO FLOOD ZONE,  spacious new home, natural lighting throughout, first-floor master bedroom and bath, interior laundry, 2 car garage with alley access and lots of guest parking, paver back patio, several outdoor lounge areas, all hurricane proof windows, doors and so much more! Schedule your showing today!
